  description: "\'Avast, me hearties, and listen to me tales o\' monsters that lair in the vastness of \\Place{wildspace} and the fiery streams o\' the \\Place{phlogiston}. Great and terrible beasties they be, just waitin\' for a daring band o\' adventurers to stumble upon \'em---or seek \'em out! Here\'s a toast to those brave enough to face the challenge!\' Place{Wildspace} and the \\Place{phlogiston} are vast. Even when ships travel at spelljamming speed, a journey can take months to complete. Now a Dungeon Master can inject the unexpected into those days when \'nothing happens\' with the exciting encounters found in \\Product{Space Lairs}. Like the original Advanced Dungeons & Dragons \\Product{Book of Lairs}, this collection contains 14 intriguing and innovative mini-adventures that can be\ninserted into any \\Product{Spelljammer} campaign with little or no\npreparation by the Dungeon Master. Featuring \\Product{Spelljammer} monsters from the \\Product{Monstrous Compendium}, these adventures provide challenges suitable for players of all levels. From puzzle-solving to action from humor to high adventure, it\'s all here in this 64-page accessory for the \\Product{Spelljammer campaign setting}. The Product{Spelljammer Adventurers in Space boxed set} is needed to use this book. So, come aboard, take the \\Item{helm}, and prepare to meet PC{Blackleg Bart} and lots of other fantastic adversaries! "
